SQL query of the view VPRT_PRT_PERFIL_ATUACAO

SELECT PRT.PRT_ID, PRT.PRT_ID_POSTERIOR, PRT.CON_ID, PRT.PRT_CD_BLOQUEADO, PRT.PRT_CD_OPER_ALTERACAO, PRT.PRT_CD_OPER_ENCAMINHAMENTO, PRT.PRT_CD_OPER_PUBLICACAO, PRT.PRT_DH_ALTERACAO, PRT.PRT_DH_ENCAMINHAMENTO, PRT.PRT_DH_PUBLICACAO, DOA.DOA_AN_CONTEUDO
FROM sup.PRT_PERFIL_ATUACAO_CON PRT
INNER JOIN SUP.DOA_DOCUMENTO_APS DOA ON DOA.DOA_ID = PRT.DOA_ID
WHERE PRT.PRT_CD_STATUS = 1
AND (PRT.PRT_DH_PUBLICACAO >= '2015-01-01' AND PRT.PRT_DH_PUBLICACAO < '2018-01-01')
